These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, november, may, december
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, peach, plum, radish
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, fonseca, chaman, montecristo
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, azure, lavender, decembercher
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, funk, r&b
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, animation, documentary, zombie
 1. the person who likes decembercher is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is the fan of classical##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 4. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is the person eating radish##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
 7. the person who likes lavender is between the person watching satire movies and the fan of r&b##2
 8. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
10. the person watching satire movies is between the person who likes lavender and the person eating radish##2
11. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
12. the person who likes decembercher is the montecristo-smoker##1
13. the fan of funk is between the fan of dubstep and the chaman-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Birthday      | december        | november       | may  | july |
| Food          | radish     | plum         | peach     | broccoli    |
| Cigar         | fonseca  | dannemann      | chaman   | montecristo     |
| Color           | azure | lilac | lavender   | decembercher     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep    | funk         | classical | r&b         |
| Movie-Genre         | zombie     | satire     | animation  | documentary       |

