 1. the egyptian is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 2. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
 4. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the russian##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who likes blue##1
 6. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1
