 8. the person who likes lilac is the person who growsazalea##1
 9. the person who likes ebony is between the person driving the van and the person who growspoppy##2
10. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
11. the person who likes pink is the person driving the subway##1
12. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person driving the skateboard##1
13. the person who growsdaisy is between the person traveling to colone and the egyptian##2

