 7. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 8. the person driving the subway is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 9. the person driving the car is between the person who growsdahlia and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
10. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
11. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person driving the car##1
12. the person who growslily is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
13. the owner of the horse is the owner of the horse##1
