The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, lawyer, firefighter, dressmaker
4 different pets are kept: lizard, goldfish, frog, dog
 1. the dutch is the wooden house##1
 2. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1
 3. the doctor is on the right of the fan of rock##1
 4. the person watching superhero movies is between the owner of the frog and the person watching spy movies##2
 5. the argentine is the firefighter##1
 6. the owner of the frog is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 7. the dressmaker is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
 9. the tower house is on the far left##1
10. the doctor is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
11. the doctor is on the right of the fan of rock##1
12. the colombian is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
13. the cottage house is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
