 3. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who growsmarigold and the person eating orange##2
 4. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 5. the fan of disco is on the far left##1
 6. the person who growsbellflower is the fan of disco##1
 7. the person drinking juice is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 8. the fan of disco is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 9. the fan of disco is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
10. the person who's sport is basketball is the fan of classical##1
11. the person drinking juice is the person eating peach##1
12. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
